The Bonus is reported under “Short-term variable compensation” as “due compensation” since the underlying services were fully rendered by the end of each period (September 30). Therefore, the Bonus payout amounts for the reporting year are reported, although payout only occurs after the end of each reporting year, in order to make reporting transparent and comprehensible and in order to guarantee a connection between performance and compensation in the reporting period.

Furthermore, in fiscal 2023 and fiscal 2022, the Stock Awards from the 2019 and 2018 tranches allocated in fiscal 2019 and fiscal 2018, respectively, became due and were settled by transfer of Siemens shares. The value of Siemens shares at the time of transfer is reported under “Long-term variable compensation.”